data.description: NEW PRICE! MOTIVATED SELLER! Beautiful 3 bedrooms cottage! Stunning curb appeal. Vaulted ceilings with mounted sound around speakers system, granite countertops, decor backsplash, custom cabinets, nickel hardware, Stain steel appliances package: Stove, dishwasher, microwave & refrigerator. 16 inch ceramic title floors w diamond granite insets; New laminate floor in  two rooms and new carpet in third room; ceiling fans, double French doors. Large back yard w covered patio, 8ft privacy fence w metal posts, 8 ft carport, storage shed; covered front porch, sprinkler system. New safe energy windows and boiler. Washer and dryer convey with the house.
